GOLFSHOT COUNTER

Description:
A simple tool for the golf round, to keep track of golfshots for each hole the intire golfround.


How to Use:
"Current hole" display: Shows the number of golfshots on the current hole.
GOLFSHOTS: Click on the "+" or "-" to increment/decrement golfshots to the count of golfshots.
NEXT HOLE: Click the "Next HOLE" button when finish adding golfshots for current hole, ready for the next hole.
"Golfshots per hole" display: Shows the count for golfshots on each hole.
"Total shots" Display: Displays the total count of golfshots for the golf round.
Reset Button: Click on the "Reset" button to reset the count to zero and ready to start new round.
